e brain immediately post-mortem." SOURCES: Independent, Resuscitationhttps://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/mind-works-after-death-consciousness-sam-parnia-nyu-langone-a8007101.htmlhttp://www.resuscitationjournal.com/article/S0300-9572(14)00739-4/abstract***For story suggestions please contact tips@nextanimation.com.twFor technical and editorial support, please contact:Asia: +61 2 93 73 1841Europe: +44 20 7542 7599Americas and Latam: +1 800 738 8377]]></description>
